Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,無生命反應
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:01.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,貨物是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:07.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:19.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:31.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:41.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:50.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:55.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗這麼說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:00.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:02.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,也許是一種防衛本能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,但具體緣由至今無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:06.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:08.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,那一天在那一個森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:13.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,她叫了我父親
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,----op----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:26.82,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何なんだろう　この胸のモヤモヤは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:26.82,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}心中的這份躁動  是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:34.58,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}洗いたてのタオルに顔を埋めるような
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:34.58,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}就像將臉埋入剛洗過的毛巾一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:41.71,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥が鳴いている　朝焼けのメロディー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:41.71,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥兒們吟唱著  朝霞的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:52.77,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どこまで歩いても　この道は続いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:52.77,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}無論走到哪  這道路都會延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:03:01.87,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手を繋ぐよりも　指を繋ぐような
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:03:01.87,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比起手牽手  更像是緊握這手指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:08.64,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒い夜は寄り添い合って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:08.64,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒冷的夜晚彼此相依
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:14.00,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}星空の毛布で眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:14.00,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}以星空為毯子安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:19.24,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}テーブルの向こうの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:19.24,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}餐桌對面的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:27.68,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}最果ての地を君と目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:27.68,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}為你指向盡頭之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:37.19,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}ありがとうはこっちの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:37.19,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我才該說謝謝你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:55.88,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,850)\blur6\pos(1625.333,1063.067)}幼子和綠岩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:01.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類  離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:05.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,這座森林不是外人的居所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:07.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,我不是你的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:13.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,中止你的跟蹤  離開森林
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:44.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,不能干涉外物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:59.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個人類的小孩會餓死  還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:14.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  那個小孩不是管理對象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:18.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的職責只有管理森林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,我找到爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,禁止你之後的跟蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:43.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,若再嘗試接近  我將會強制排除你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,立刻離開這座森林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:53.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,你本來不在我的管理下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,攝取完之後就離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,攝取？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,咬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:22.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類的小孩  我理解了你不想離開森林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是  至少說明下理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:30.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,因為別人說外面很危險所以不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是誰的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,你原先在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,你的名字是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:42.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣什麼也解決不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:45.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,那你的父母在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,絕對不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:00.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,我不明白這些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,不明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,話語的意義能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是沒有共感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:11.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,守護人只會根據規定好的事件行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,並管理森林
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:16.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,是只為了森林而存活的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,不寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:22.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆沒有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:26.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,因此只會一個人在森林徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們會一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:45.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:46.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:01.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,枷鎖的聲音會讓野獸警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,這句話是多餘的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,我去抓魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:23.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:29.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:46.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:53.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是爸爸的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:59.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是脫落下來的  沒有問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,我不要爸爸壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:04.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,你該適可而止了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,那不會再接合上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:11.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,比起這個  你該反省下溺死的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,你的行動是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:18.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的活動時間所剩無幾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:42.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,我消失後  這個人類在森林裡生存下去的可能性極低
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,要離開森林？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:50.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:53.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,要將你送回人類身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:56.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,現在處於溫暖時期也能旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:00.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,關於你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,哇  貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  那隻野獸的名字是「深綠索瑪麗」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:10.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,是它最先找到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:13.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:21.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,借用它的名字  從今天開始你就叫做索瑪麗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:22.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,對  索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:36.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,那就是我和索瑪麗的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:39.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,以及踏上旅途原委
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:46.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆  你剩下的時間還有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:54.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,如果可以的話  能讓我看看你現在的身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:57.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,表皮只剩下這些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,內部的肉出現了龜裂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,體液也在流失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,一個月前  關節處也開始咯吱響
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:23.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,往後  如果我的身體崩壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:25.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,我希望把索瑪麗託付給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,我很樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:31.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是  你覺得這樣就好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:34.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,拖著殘破不堪的身軀走到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:36.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,只是因為義務嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,和索瑪麗踏上旅途後  現在我才懂得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,其實原因  從最開始就很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:51.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,我只是想一直看著她的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:55.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,那麼就不能夠放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:02.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,其實這之後  你也想待在她的身邊守護著她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:24.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,要不要再去睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,一大早就這麼沒精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,喝口茶醒個神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:42.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,是從今天開始吧  當旅館的保鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:45.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  約定好了七天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:50.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,工作是懲治品行不端的客人  就我們兩個人做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,飯做好了  想吃了就吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃完記得打掃房間  別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:57.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:02.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,本來我是想留下來看家的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,我會照看索瑪麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗經常不顧左右
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:16.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,眼前要是有好奇的事物就會衝上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,希望你注意一下不要讓她摔著了撞著了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,還有  關於喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,她不喜歡帶有苦澀味道的蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是也要考慮到營養均衡  不能妥協
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:31.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,這些夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是的  這也太保護過度了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:35.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:40.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒事的  交給錫佐我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:43.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,趕緊趕緊  一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,十分不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:14:59.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:08.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,錫佐  雪好大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:09.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:10.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆他們去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:17.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,對哦  說是要去當保鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,對的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以今天你和我留下來看家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,趕緊來吃早飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:26.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃完過後索瑪麗打算幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗想…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:40.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,平時都是和爸爸玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:43.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:45.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:48.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,我想送爸爸禮物  感謝平時對我的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,挺不錯的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是要對爸爸保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,禮物  禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:04.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,送爸爸  禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,禮物…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:09.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,完成啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:16.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,完成了嗎  畫像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,遇到麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:21.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,我覺得挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,挺不錯是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,必須要100滿分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,換成其它的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,其它的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,一起邊打掃衛生邊想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:36.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:42.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:50.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼啊  迎接方式這麼誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,才不誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:53.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:58.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,第一次分別了這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:16:59.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,那就不奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,話說真是太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,客人們的吵架稀鬆平常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃霸王餐的還有偷東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,還好我們是兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,要是只有我可忙不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:21.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,多虧了你們倆  還給發了工資
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,反而還挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:25.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,你好意思說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:27.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:31.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,店主說明天會送物資到我們這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,物資  是食物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:35.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:38.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,因為下雪購買東西太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,反正是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:42.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,麻煩你們接收一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:46.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:50.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,今天的衛生弄得真馬虎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,明天弄好一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗也要幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:58.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:11.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,有沒有好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:16.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒事吧  索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,在想事情沒注意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:26.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,工具也齊全  來編織東西吧  索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:29.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是索瑪麗不會編織…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:32.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒關係  我教你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,那好  我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:38.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過要編織什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,昨天說的物資嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,來了  你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,哇  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,你就是他們說的小孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:55.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個…我已經成年了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:58.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,小孩子是在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,哎呀不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,我是店主的妻子羅扎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:06.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,你們可以叫我羅扎阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:11.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,這麼多  可以收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:16.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,可以的  丈夫昨天可是誇讚你們幫了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以你們多吃點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:21.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,咦  是在編織什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:25.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗想給送禮物給她爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:28.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是還在想該送什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:33.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,手環怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:36.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:40.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,手環作為編織物很暢銷的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們店裡也有在賣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,被稱作是最幸運的手鐲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:49.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,飽含著製作者祝願幸福的寓意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:52.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是  索瑪麗能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:58.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,有一種叫三色編的  連小孩子都能夠輕鬆編織
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:01.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,來挑選三個喜歡的顏色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:05.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,那  這個和這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:07.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,還有要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:14.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,然後將三色的毛線紮起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,右邊的放到中間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:20.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,之後將左邊的線放在上邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:22.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,最後在內部相交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,不斷重複就行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,很簡單對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,慢慢地不要著急
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,不斷將毛線交錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,好厲害  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,太好了  索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆肯定也會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:41.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:46.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,包含的情感越是強烈  就編織得越是結實喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:49.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以要好好地編織
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:51.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我會好好地編織
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是個乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,羅扎阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,也教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:08.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,你要選什麼顏色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:27.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:30.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,亞巴希你也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:33.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,這些話從哪兒學來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,看上去挺興奮的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,發生什麼了嗎  索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:43.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是難得一見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:55.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,那傢伙肯定能買很多錢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是在耍我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:00.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,絕對沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:04.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,那就是人類的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:22.98,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}並ぶ影の大きさ比べ笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:22.98,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比較著並排的影子相視而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:26.55,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}夕暮れを背に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:26.55,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}把夕陽甩在身後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:37.62,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}そっと風に乗せたのは　まだ小さな願い事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:37.62,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}乘風而去的是那小小的祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:44.65,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}永遠とか　生命だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:44.65,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}什麼是永遠  什麼是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:49.25,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何も分からずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:49.25,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我還一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:23:01.53,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}真っ直ぐな瞳で　見上げた横顔は眩しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:23:01.53,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}只知道當我抬頭仰望你時  你的側臉總是那麼地閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:07.88,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}重ねた手に伝う温もりは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:07.88,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手牽著手傳遞的這份溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:12.40,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どんなときも愛をくれたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:12.40,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}無論何時都在給予我愛意
